snippet.title: City Of The Dead Game
snippet.description:
This is the trailer for city of the dead zombie game, sadly it got cancelled.

Update 2: This game has now been released but under a different title, search for "Day Of The Zombie" on torrents or rapidshare, the story has been changed but i think everything else has remained the same.

http://www.freshdl.com/games/3/day-of-the-zombie-2009-full.html

Update 1: i spoke to my friend James who works for Kuju entertainment & they were the guys that were developing the game, apparently the distributor went bust & the project was stopped & never got a release, too bad because it looks like a fun game.

http://www.kuju.com/
